Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.97,0:00:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在回想起来，自从那天以来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.14,0:00:27.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来过这里多少次了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.11,0:00:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.58,0:00:31.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个国度
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.38,0:00:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，在这个星球\N我思念的只有一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.95,0:00:38.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那小小的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.25,0:00:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.25,0:00:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是我和千濑的定情之处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.17,0:01:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在那天，从这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.54,0:01:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这个地方开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（阿修）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.65,0:01:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:50.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.01,0:02:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动作会不会太慢了啊，千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.18,0:02:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.75,0:02:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.70,0:02:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是慢吞吞的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.93,0:02:38.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,个子又小，胆子也很小
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且又笨手笨脚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.71,0:02:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成绩也只有中下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:45.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有世界史好得莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.48,0:02:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这无法成为\N将来谋生的一技之长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.71,0:02:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她自己也很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.55,0:02:55.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:02:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.50,0:03:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的口头禅是“对不起”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的座右铭是\N“想要变得更坚强”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.07,0:03:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么看都觉得是个\N没有用的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:18.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.14,0:03:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.15,0:03:25.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.95,0:03:27.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天还是像以前一样\N搭公交车上学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.82,0:03:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想跟我一起爬地狱坡\N是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊，不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:40.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟我不久以前还是田径队的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.94,0:03:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是，我还是得跟你一起上学才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为，我是你的女朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.28,0:03:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.28,0:04:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交换日记？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.46,0:04:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然不喜欢吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.86,0:04:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁怂恿你做这种事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是明美他们吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我真的想多了解你一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，你们两个\N不快点就会迟到喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明美，早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:34.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又在欺负千濑吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.95,0:04:36.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没有欺负她！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，要迟到了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法，我就陪你写吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以快点走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的女朋友，千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五天前她向我表白\N要我跟她交往
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.56,0:05:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.59,0:05:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在依然犹豫不决
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.67,0:05:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交换日记啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦，你就陪她写吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正晚上\N也没有什么事情可以做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.88,0:05:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电视老是在回放\N不然就是放电影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说手机跟网络\N现在又不能用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我该写什么好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛，比如说\N你今天一整天做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:46.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是去了什么地方之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.89,0:05:52.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正到了暑假\N就不会一直在一起了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.43,0:05:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了学校和家里之外\N我还有什么地方能去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.53,0:05:59.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然你就写\N你喜欢千濑什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是想跟她接吻\N想跟她嘿咻之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说这个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿竹，你跟由佳利上床了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯，毕竟我们交往两个月了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.45,0:06:14.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然已经上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.09,0:06:14.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来听嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不说\N因为说了会被你们当笑柄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.15,0:06:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点点就好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，等等我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去捡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.23,0:06:27.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:31.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑，修次在看你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.17,0:06:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊，明美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.74,0:06:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向她挥挥手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然又会被明美臭骂喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,F-15
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近经常在飞耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会是发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说东京和大阪那边挺危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:04.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会有事的啦，反正跟我们无关
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交换日记啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.31,0:07:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，你现在在做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在当然是在看日记啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.92,0:07:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我提起勇气向你告白\N真的是做对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在每天都过得好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想…千濑，你好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.17,0:07:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假就快要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么计划…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.08,0:07:50.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在搞什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，你在睡觉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.63,0:08:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我醒着啦，现在就去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.57,0:08:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟女生交往，原来这么麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，我们要先吃啰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.69,0:08:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是够了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要一直叫我阿修啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.71,0:08:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里可以随便进去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:09:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会被骂吗？这是基地里面耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系，反正只是基地的边缘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.49,0:09:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前都可以自由进出的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他终于把交换日记还你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.37,0:09:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了，千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.71,0:09:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（还是算了吧不过放学后陪我一下）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不出所料\N我可以了解修次的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.98,0:09:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放学后…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是指“嘿咻”吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，我们没迷路吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里半个人都没有耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得现在还太早…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.11,0:10:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后我想让你看看这个景色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.21,0:10:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉，我已经累了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.52,0:10:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这个人不适合谈恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.63,0:10:50.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，并不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.77,0:11:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也觉得很累啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道男女交往\N该做些什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.51,0:11:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拼命的问明美\N还看了一堆漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:13.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试着去做好多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.58,0:11:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全无法像别人一样\N顺利的谈恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,归根究底都是你的错啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.73,0:11:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.13,0:11:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我根本就没想要跟你交往！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是为了试试胆量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.77,0:11:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改变我软弱的个性
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.35,0:11:47.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为明美知道我一直很崇拜你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.05,0:11:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就叫我向你表白\N想说失败也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道你竟然答应跟我交往
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般都会答应吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:11:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要答应我？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你这么可爱的女孩告白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家当然会答应啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:13.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你向人家告白前\N人家根本没打算和女生交往
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.95,0:12:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.01,0:12:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“人家”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.39,0:12:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从小时候就这样说话\N这有什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，你好可爱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜！你比较可爱啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:36.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.33,0:12:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实，我真的很怕你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.59,0:12:56.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要一直说对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.12,0:12:58.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.93,0:13:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交往至今\N我好像是第一次看到你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.75,0:13:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许男女交往就像这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.26,0:13:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还是男朋友和女朋友吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然顺序有点混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:50.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得有缘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后我们要不要\N试着去喜欢对方看看？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:14:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.49,0:14:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.73,0:14:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，写吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:16.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，你希望我对你做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了，我做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:51.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们打算从这里\N开始我们的恋情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:15:00.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的心脏跳得好大声喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:03.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.78,0:15:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个乡下的小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.52,0:15:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然没有任何乐趣可言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.95,0:15:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对未来也是茫茫然的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们两人\N已经决定了一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要继续相恋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.20,0:15:26.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以偶尔打电话给你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.81,0:15:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊\N路上小心点，不要跌倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.18,0:15:34.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，咖啡卖完了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.92,0:16:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.96,0:16:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.10,0:16:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由佳利和阿竹在吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.54,0:16:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜，不要随便认定\N他们是在吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.94,0:16:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，我向你道歉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.32,0:16:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个伤怎么来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又在家里跌倒了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.79,0:16:55.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么，不要紧的，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:16:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的很粗心大意耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:17:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微小心一点喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.53,0:17:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟你是个女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，我们两个也会吵架吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.08,0:17:16.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该吵不起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.09,0:17:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你经常哼这首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜欢这首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.99,0:17:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.77,0:17:42.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我们要代替那个\N最后突然说不来的千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:45.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陪你来札幌大采购呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.84,0:17:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少废话，闭上你的嘴巴快选啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:49.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.31,0:17:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没女朋友还要来买服饰\N只是更空虚而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.42,0:17:55.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要请我吃烤玉米喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猪头，你是观光客啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.69,0:18:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是玫瑰水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.49,0:18:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是爱与疗伤的宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.33,0:18:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好喔，我也要买给我女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.20,0:18:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们两个吵架还没和好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.91,0:18:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是地震
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.08,0:18:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，这个地震很强喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.11,0:18:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像越来越近了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:26.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，去外面看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.78,0:18:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要出去，阿淳\N这时候乱跑很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.95,0:18:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊，避难训练时学过了不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.16,0:18:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猪头，别在这里说风凉话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.53,0:18:45.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是哪里的战斗机？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.17,0:18:49.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我们国家的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:18:58.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底出了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.25,0:19:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之往大道公园逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊，这里太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿淳，你看上面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是F-2，从三泽来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.47,0:19:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往这里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.37,0:19:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次，快点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.24,0:19:21.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个钟楼才刚刚修好的说．
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.04,0:19:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿律，快逃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:31.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，修次，阿律，阿竹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.06,0:19:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.47,0:19:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么？到底是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿竹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.07,0:19:55.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿竹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿竹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:19:57.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿竹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.84,0:20:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿竹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.98,0:20:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿竹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.02,0:20:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿竹，喂，阿竹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:11.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿竹，你不可以死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.49,0:20:13.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来救救他，来人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.19,0:21:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:24.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身体变成了这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.52,0:21:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在回想起来\N那时候我应该察觉到才对
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.51,0:22:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.91,0:22:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我抱着千濑\N她的心脏却没有心跳声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.15,0:22:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,#01 我们将继续相恋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.60,0:22:43.51,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心中有一道裂缝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.57,0:22:50.45,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,难以入眠的夜里总不停的叹息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.51,0:23:00.15,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不觉黎明已悄然到来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.23,0:23:09.06,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,多么想听见你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.13,0:23:13.16,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,感受你的体温
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.24,0:23:20.47,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,对你的思念越来越强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:25.21,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,泪水夺眶而出
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.28,0:23:30.35,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了我心爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.42,0:23:36.55,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,我仍无法忘怀你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.63,0:23:41.46,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然只因一句再见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.53,0:23:46.97,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,就要结束一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.04,0:23:52.10,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,叫人感到悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.35,0:24:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑，你说你变成终极武器\N是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.35,0:24:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要上战场打仗一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.16,0:24:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还只是高中生耶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.12,0:24:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.39,0:24:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终兵器彼女下一回\N「我正在成长」
